<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.5">
<l>aṇṭamumiv valaikaṭalu mavaṉikaḷuṅ kulavaraiyum</l>
<l>uṇṭapirā ṉuṟaiyumiṭa moḷimaṇican takilkaṉakam</l>
<l>teṇṭiraikaḷ varattiraṭṭum tikaḻmaṇṇit teṉkaraimēl</l>
<l>tiṇtiṟalār payilnāṅkait tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where dwells the lord who consumed the universe,</l>
<l rend="indent">this crashing sea, worlds,</l>
<l>And mountain ranges is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai in Nāṅkai</l>
<l>Where strong, courageous [people] dwell on the southern shore</l>
<l rend="indent">of the glittering Maṇṇi [River]</l>
<l>Where shining jewels, sandal and aquila wood, and gold mound up</l>
<l rend="indent">as crystal waves advance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
